@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <section>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>At Recipe Book, we believe that cooking should be accessible to everyone—from beginners who are just learning to chop an onion to advanced cooks...</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2024 by TU Varna students, Recipe Book started as a small blog inspired by a passion for sustainable cooking and a desire to share delicious, easy-to-follow recipes. Today, we are a thriving community of cooks and food enthusiasts from around the world. Our team is made up of professional chefs, home cooks, and culinary instructors who are dedicated to bringing you the best cooking content.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Daily Recipes</li>
            <li>Cooking Tips & Techniques</li>
            <li>Video Tutorials</li>
            <li>Community Engagement</li>
            <li>Seasonal and Festive Dishes</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <p>Passion for Food, Inclusivity, Education, Community</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have questions, suggestions, or want to join our team? We’d love to hear from you! Contact us at contact@email.com or follow us on our social media pages at [Facebook, Instagram, Twitter].</p>
    </section>
</div>
